    <item>
      <title>微软称拜登退出竞选后俄罗斯影响力运动转向哈里斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/russian-election-propaganda-targets-harris-microsoft-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[微软公司的最新研究显示，在总统乔·拜登结束重返白宫的竞选活动后，俄罗斯影响美国大选的行动转向利用篡改和误导性视频抹黑副总统卡马拉·哈里斯。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/russian-election-propaganda-targets-harris-microsoft-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Snap 推出新款眼镜，助力增强现实</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/snap-unveils-new-smart-glasses-in-revived-augmented-reality-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Snap Inc. 首席执行官埃文·斯皮格尔 (Evan Spiegel) 发布了该公司 Spectacles 智能眼镜的新版本，重新激发了打造先进增强现实产品的努力，该产品未来可能取代或与智能手机相媲美。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/snap-unveils-new-smart-glasses-in-revived-augmented-reality-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
