      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/jpmorgan-joins-suitors-for-apple-card-that-goldman-wants-to-shed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通公司正在与苹果公司商谈接管其竞争对手高盛集团一直试图放弃的信用卡业务。]]></description>
